any of <cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="act" value="Terrorism Risk Insurance Act of 2002/s:103/ss:e/p:6/sp:A..E">subparagraphs (A) through (E) of paragraph (6)</cato:entity-ref>, terrorism loss risk-spreading premiums in an
